snippet.title: Friction - Gameplay Video 02
snippet.description:
Friction is a gun shooting game where players must navigate through three challenging levels full of varied gameplay and enemies. The 3D rail shooter is the first game developed by newly formed Friction Game Studios.

for more information. Please visit 
http://www.highwaygames.com/products/view.php?id=3681
